TY  - JOUR
TI  - More Efficient Estimation in the Presence of Heteroscedasticity of Unknown Form
AU  - Cragg, J. G.
AB  - [Recent work on inference in regressions with heteroscedastic disturbances leads to the possibility of more efficient estimators. The conditions needed to exploit the possibility are discussed. A sampling experiment indicates that the gains can be achieved even in small samples.]
